彗星的核心固體結構稱為彗核，是由[[冰|水冰]]、[[岩石|岩石]]、和凍結的氣體（如[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]、[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]、[[甲烷|甲烷]]和[[氨|氨]]等）融合在一起組成的<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Making a comet nucleus|url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1998A&A...330..375G/abstract|last=Greenberg|first=J. Mayo|date=1998-02|journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics|volume=330|pages=375–380|language=en|issn=0004-6361|access-date=2022-06-26|archive-date=2022-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408043134/https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1998A%26A...330..375G/abstract}}</ref>。1950年代，[[美國|美國]][[天文學家|天文學家]][[弗雷德·惠普爾|弗雷德·惠普爾]]提出「彗星的內核是由含冰的凝聚物組成」的假說，這個「彗星模型」後來令彗星普遍的被大眾（包含惠普爾本人）暱稱為「冰污球」（Icy dirtballs）或「髒雪球」（Dirty Snowballs）<ref>{{cite web|title=Dirty Snowballs in Space|url=http://starryskies.com/solar_system/Comet/dirty_snowballs.html|accessdate=2013-08-15|publisher=Starryskies|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130129035627/http://starryskies.com/solar_system/Comet/dirty_snowballs.html|archive-date=2013-01-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/news/evidence-from-esas-rosetta-spacecraft-suggests-that-comets-are-more-icy-dirtball-than-dirty-snowball/199168.article|title=Evidence from ESA's Rosetta Spacecraft Suggests that Comets are more "Icy Dirtball" than "Dirty Snowball"|date=2005-10-21|work=Times Higher Education|accessdate=2014-05-21|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014172656/http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/news/evidence-from-esas-rosetta-spacecraft-suggests-that-comets-are-more-icy-dirtball-than-dirty-snowball/199168.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

彗核的表面一般是乾燥、塵土或岩石飛揚的，這暗示冰是隱藏在表面數公尺厚的的地殼之下。除了已經提到的氣體，彗核還包含各種各樣的[[有機化合物|有機化合物]]，它們可能包括[[甲醇|甲醇]]、[[氰化氫|氰化氫]]、[[甲醛|甲醛]]、[[乙醇|乙醇]]、和[[乙烷|乙烷]]，或許還有更複雜的分子，如長鏈的[[烴類|烴類]]和[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]<ref>{{cite web|title=1997 Apparition of Comet Hale–Bopp: What We Can Learn from Bright Comets|url=http://www.psrd.hawaii.edu/Feb97/Bright.html|accessdate=2013-04-30|date=1997-03-24|last=Meech|first=M.|publisher=Planetary Science Research Discoveries|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GjrCCXsq?url=http://www.psrd.hawaii.edu/Feb97/Bright.html|archive-date=2013-05-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Stardust Findings Suggest Comets More Complex Than Thought|url=http://stardust.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news110.html|accessdate=2013-07-31|date=2006-12-14|publisher=NASA|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gjr11its?url=http://stardust.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news110.html|archive-date=2013-05-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在 2009年，從NASA[[星塵號|星塵任務]]帶回的彗星[[塵埃|塵埃]]中發現了氨基酸中的[[甘氨酸|甘氨酸]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Cometary glycine detected in samples returned by Stardust|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1945-5100.2009.tb01224.x|last=Elsila|first=Jamie E.|last2=Glavin|first2=Daniel P.|date=2009-09|journal=Meteoritics & Planetary Science|issue=9|doi=10.1111/j.1945-5100.2009.tb01224.x|volume=44|pages=1323–1330|language=en|last3=Dworkin|first3=Jason P.|access-date=2021-12-16|archive-date=2022-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220421173520/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1945-5100.2009.tb01224.x}}</ref>。在2011年8月，[[美国国家航空航天局|NASA]]一份根據在[[地球|地球]]上發現的[[隕石|隕石]]所做的報告指出，已經發現[[脱氧核糖核酸|DNA]]和[[核糖核酸|RNA]]的元件（[[腺嘌呤|腺嘌呤]]、[[鳥嘌呤|鳥嘌呤]]、及相關的[[有機分子|有機分子]]），可能已經在[[小行星|小行星]]和彗星上形成<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Carbonaceous meteorites contain a wide range of extraterrestrial nucleobases|url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.1106493108|last=Callahan|first=M. P.|last2=Smith|first2=K. E.|date=2011-08-23|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=34|doi=10.1073/pnas.1106493108|volume=108|pages=13995–13998|language=en|issn=0027-8424|last3=Cleaves|first3=H. J.|last4=Ruzicka|first4=J.|last5=Stern|first5=J. C.|last6=Glavin|first6=D. P.|last7=House|first7=C. H.|last8=Dworkin|first8=J. P.}}</ref><ref name="Steigerwald">{{cite web|title=NASA Researchers: DNA Building Blocks Can Be Made in Space|url=http://www.nasa.gov/topics/solarsystem/features/dna-meteorites.html|accessdate=2013-07-31|date=2011-08-08|last=Steigerwald|first=John|publisher=NASA|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150623004556/http://www.nasa.gov/topics/solarsystem/features/dna-meteorites.html|archive-date=2015-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

彗核表面的[[反照率|反照率]]非常的低，使它們成為太陽系內反照率最低的物體。[[喬托號|喬托號]][[太空探測器|太空探測器]]發現[[哈雷彗星|哈雷彗星]]的彗核只反射了大約4%照射在它上面的光線<ref name="dark">{{Cite journal|title=The Activity and Size of the Nucleus of Comet Hale-Bopp (C/1995 O1)|url=https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.275.5308.1900|last=Weaver|first=H. A.|last2=Feldman|first2=P. D.|date=1997-03-28|journal=Science|issue=5308|doi=10.1126/science.275.5308.1900|volume=275|pages=1900–1904|language=en|issn=0036-8075|last3=A'Hearn|first3=M. F.|last4=Arpigny|first4=C.|last5=Brandt|first5=J. C.|last6=Festou|first6=M. C.|last7=Haken|first7=M.|last8=McPhate|first8=J. B.|last9=Stern|first9=S. A.|access-date=2021-12-16|archive-date=2022-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405014943/https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.275.5308.1900}}</ref>，[[深空一號|深空一號]]發現[[包瑞利彗星|包瑞利彗星]]表面反射落在它上面的光線少於3%<ref name="dark" />；相較之下，落在[[瀝青|瀝青]]表面的光都還有7%能被反射。彗核表面黑暗的物質材料可能包括複雜的[[有機化合物|有機化合物]]。太陽的熱驅動了較輕的[[揮發性|揮發物]]，留下了較重的有機化合物，往往都是黑色的，像是[[焦油|焦油]]或是[[石油|原油]]。彗星表面相對較低的反照率使它們可以吸收更多需要的熱量，驅動[[釋氣|釋氣]]的程序<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PRqVqQKao9QC&pg=PA91|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|date=2008-11-14|isbn=978-3-540-76945-3|language=en|first=Arnold|last=Hanslmeier|title=Habitability and Cosmic Catastrophes|pages=91|access-date=2021-12-16|archive-date=2022-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220411192510/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PRqVqQKao9QC&pg=PA91}}</ref>。

